{
  "id": "6a157e63d574e00a56afcd9b",
  "title": "弱い Bot が混在しても成立する多人数ゲームジャンルの条件",
  "created": 1779793525,
  "updated": 1779798539,
  "lines": [
    {
      "id": "6a157e63d574e00a56afcd9b",
      "text": "弱い Bot が混在しても成立する多人数ゲームジャンルの条件",
      "userId": "586cfba1be83a60011cafbcd",
      "created": 1779793525,
      "updated": 1779793525
    },
    {
      "id": "6a157e6b000000000017ddbf",
      "text": "[tokoroten.icon]のClaudeのログから自動抽出された記事",
      "userId": "586cfba1be83a60011cafbcd",
      "created": 1779793525,
      "updated": 1779793548
    },
    {
      "id": "6a157e70000000000017de23",
      "text": "----",
      "userId": "586cfba1be83a60011cafbcd",
      "created": 1779793530,
      "updated": 1779793532
    },
    {
      "id": "6a157e71000000000017de24",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "586cfba1be83a60011cafbcd",
      "created": 1779793530,
      "updated": 1779793530
    },
    {
      "id": "6a157e6b000000000017ddc3",
      "text": "ソーシャルゲームのマッチング過疎時間帯を Bot で埋めたい。",
      "userId": "586cfba1be83a60011cafbcd",
      "created": 1779793525,
      "updated": 1779793525
    },
    {
      "id": "6a157e6b000000000017ddc4",
      "text": "バトロワでは弱 Bot が即バレるが、ホールデムや麻雀では Bot が",
      "userId": "586cfba1be83a60011cafbcd",
      "created": 1779793525,
      "updated": 1779793525
    },
    {
      "id": "6a157e6b000000000017ddc5",
      "text": "プレイヤーにチップを流す存在として[* 自然に機能]する。",
      "userId": "586cfba1be83a60011cafbcd",
      "created": 1779793525,
      "updated": 1779793525
    },
    {
      "id": "6a157e6b000000000017ddc6",
      "text": "この差を生む構造を整理する。",
      "userId": "586cfba1be83a60011cafbcd",
      "created": 1779793525,
      "updated": 1779793525
    },
    {
      "id": "6a157e6b000000000017ddc7",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "586cfba1be83a60011cafbcd",
      "created": 1779793525,
      "updated": 1779793525
    },
    {
      "id": "6a157e6b000000000017ddc8",
      "text": "[*** 弱 Bot が溶け込む 3 条件]",
      "userId": "586cfba1be83a60011cafbcd",
      "created": 1779793525,
      "updated": 1779793525
    },
    {
      "id": "6a157e6b000000000017ddc9",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "586cfba1be83a60011cafbcd",
      "created": 1779793525,
      "updated": 1779793525
    },
    {
      "id": "6a157e6b000000000017ddca",
      "text": "[* ① 運の比重が大きい (結果の不確実性が高い)]",
      "userId": "586cfba1be83a60011cafbcd",
      "created": 1779793525,
      "updated": 1779793525
    },
    {
      "id": "6a157e6b000000000017ddcb",
      "text": "→ 「負けたのは弱いからではなく運が悪かったから」と読まれる",
      "userId": "586cfba1be83a60011cafbcd",
      "created": 1779793525,
      "updated": 1779793525
    },
    {
      "id": "6a157e6b000000000017ddcc",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "586cfba1be83a60011cafbcd",
      "created": 1779793525,
      "updated": 1779793525
    },
    {
      "id": "6a157e6b000000000017ddcd",
      "text": "[* ② 行動の正解が外から判断しにくい (情報の非対称性)]",
      "userId": "586cfba1be83a60011cafbcd",
      "created": 1779793525,
      "updated": 1779793525
    },
    {
      "id": "6a157e6b000000000017ddce",
      "text": "→ 観戦者・対戦相手から「その手は明らかに間違い」と断定できない",
      "userId": "586cfba1be83a60011cafbcd",
      "created": 1779793525,
      "updated": 1779793525
    },
    {
      "id": "6a157e6b000000000017ddcf",
      "text": "→ ホールデムの 3bet コール = 弱手か罠か外からは判らない",
      "userId": "586cfba1be83a60011cafbcd",
      "created": 1779793525,
      "updated": 1779793525
    },
    {
      "id": "6a157e6b000000000017ddd0",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "586cfba1be83a60011cafbcd",
      "created": 1779793525,
      "updated": 1779793525
    },
    {
      "id": "6a157e6b000000000017ddd1",
      "text": "[* ③ プレイスタイルの幅が広い]",
      "userId": "586cfba1be83a60011cafbcd",
      "created": 1779793525,
      "updated": 1779793525
    },
    {
      "id": "6a157e6b000000000017ddd2",
      "text": "→ 「堅実」「攻撃的」「奇策」など正当な戦略が複数あれば弱さが個性に紛れる",
      "userId": "586cfba1be83a60011cafbcd",
      "created": 1779793525,
      "updated": 1779793525
    },
    {
      "id": "6a157e6b000000000017ddd3",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "586cfba1be83a60011cafbcd",
      "created": 1779793525,
      "updated": 1779793525
    },
    {
      "id": "6a157e6b000000000017ddd4",
      "text": "[*** 相性の良いジャンル]",
      "userId": "586cfba1be83a60011cafbcd",
      "created": 1779793525,
      "updated": 1779793525
    },
    {
      "id": "6a157e6b000000000017ddd5",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "586cfba1be83a60011cafbcd",
      "created": 1779793525,
      "updated": 1779793525
    },
    {
      "id": "6a157e6b000000000017ddd6",
      "text": "\t[* オークション・競り系] (ラー、モダンアート) — 過大入札も過小入札も「価値観の違い」、弱 Bot がリソースを流す構造",
      "userId": "586cfba1be83a60011cafbcd",
      "created": 1779793525,
      "updated": 1779793525
    },
    {
      "id": "6a157e6b000000000017ddd7",
      "text": "\t[* トレーディング・交渉系] (カタン、モノポリー)",
      "userId": "586cfba1be83a60011cafbcd",
      "created": 1779793525,
      "updated": 1779793525
    },
    {
      "id": "6a157e6b000000000017ddd8",
      "text": "\t[* 不完全情報トリックテイキング] (ハーツ、スカート)",
      "userId": "586cfba1be83a60011cafbcd",
      "created": 1779793525,
      "updated": 1779793525
    },
    {
      "id": "6a157e6b000000000017ddd9",
      "text": "\t[* 株・投資・経済シミュ系] — 「バブルに乗り遅れた」「損切りが下手」が現実の失敗パターンと区別不能",
      "userId": "586cfba1be83a60011cafbcd",
      "created": 1779793525,
      "updated": 1779793525
    },
    {
      "id": "6a157e6b000000000017ddda",
      "text": "\t[* 麻雀] — 4 人打ち / 情報限定 / 打ち筋多様 / 運の比重大 / 弱者が強者にアシストする構造あり",
      "userId": "586cfba1be83a60011cafbcd",
      "created": 1779793525,
      "updated": 1779793525
    },
    {
      "id": "6a157e6b000000000017dddb",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "586cfba1be83a60011cafbcd",
      "created": 1779793525,
      "updated": 1779793525
    },
    {
      "id": "6a157e6b000000000017dddc",
      "text": "[*** 避けるべき特徴]",
      "userId": "586cfba1be83a60011cafbcd",
      "created": 1779793525,
      "updated": 1779793525
    },
    {
      "id": "6a157e6b000000000017dddd",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "586cfba1be83a60011cafbcd",
      "created": 1779793525,
      "updated": 1779793525
    },
    {
      "id": "6a157e6b000000000017ddde",
      "text": "\tリアルタイム操作精度が見える (FPS、格闘)",
      "userId": "586cfba1be83a60011cafbcd",
      "created": 1779793525,
      "updated": 1779793525
    },
    {
      "id": "6a157e6b000000000017dddf",
      "text": "\t盤面完全公開 (チェス、囲碁)",
      "userId": "586cfba1be83a60011cafbcd",
      "created": 1779793525,
      "updated": 1779793525
    },
    {
      "id": "6a157e6b000000000017dde0",
      "text": "\t行動の正解が自明 (パズル系)",
      "userId": "586cfba1be83a60011cafbcd",
      "created": 1779793525,
      "updated": 1779793525
    },
    {
      "id": "6a157e6b000000000017dde1",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "586cfba1be83a60011cafbcd",
      "created": 1779793525,
      "updated": 1779793525
    },
    {
      "id": "6a157e6b000000000017dde2",
      "text": "[*** 「バーチャル名誉」のジレンマと回避]",
      "userId": "586cfba1be83a60011cafbcd",
      "created": 1779793525,
      "updated": 1779793525
    },
    {
      "id": "6a157e6b000000000017dde3",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "586cfba1be83a60011cafbcd",
      "created": 1779793525,
      "updated": 1779793525
    },
    {
      "id": "6a157e6b000000000017dde4",
      "text": "\t架空銘柄バーチャルトレード → 名誉が生まれない",
      "userId": "586cfba1be83a60011cafbcd",
      "created": 1779793525,
      "updated": 1779793525
    },
    {
      "id": "6a157e6b000000000017dde5",
      "text": "\t現実銘柄バーチャルトレード → 本物の興奮に負ける (=送客アプリにしかなれない)",
      "userId": "586cfba1be83a60011cafbcd",
      "created": 1779793525,
      "updated": 1779793525
    },
    {
      "id": "6a157e6b000000000017dde6",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "586cfba1be83a60011cafbcd",
      "created": 1779793525,
      "updated": 1779793525
    },
    {
      "id": "6a157e6b000000000017dde7",
      "text": "反例: ポーカートーナメント / 天鳳十段",
      "userId": "586cfba1be83a60011cafbcd",
      "created": 1779793525,
      "updated": 1779793525
    },
    {
      "id": "6a157e6b000000000017dde8",
      "text": "→ 名誉は「リアルマネー」ではなく [* 希少性 × 公開性 × コミュニティ認知] の三点で成立。",
      "userId": "586cfba1be83a60011cafbcd",
      "created": 1779793525,
      "updated": 1779793525
    },
    {
      "id": "6a157e6b000000000017dde9",
      "text": "リアルマネー不要。",
      "userId": "586cfba1be83a60011cafbcd",
      "created": 1779793525,
      "updated": 1779793525
    },
    {
      "id": "6a157e6b000000000017ddea",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "586cfba1be83a60011cafbcd",
      "created": 1779793525,
      "updated": 1779793525
    },
    {
      "id": "6a157e6b000000000017ddeb",
      "text": "[*** 設計収束: 育成 × ベッティング型]",
      "userId": "586cfba1be83a60011cafbcd",
      "created": 1779793525,
      "updated": 1779793525
    },
    {
      "id": "6a157e6b000000000017ddec",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "586cfba1be83a60011cafbcd",
      "created": 1779793525,
      "updated": 1779793525
    },
    {
      "id": "6a157e6b000000000017dded",
      "text": "「予想ゲーム」(アークナイツのデュエルチャンネル型) は条件をクリアするが、",
      "userId": "586cfba1be83a60011cafbcd",
      "created": 1779793525,
      "updated": 1779793525
    },
    {
      "id": "6a157e6b000000000017ddee",
      "text": "[* 介入感の薄さ]が継続性を削ぐ (見ているだけになる)。",
      "userId": "586cfba1be83a60011cafbcd",
      "created": 1779793525,
      "updated": 1779793525
    },
    {
      "id": "6a157e6b000000000017ddef",
      "text": "→ [* 「自分が育てたモンスターを出走させる側にもなれる」] で介入感を補う。",
      "userId": "586cfba1be83a60011cafbcd",
      "created": 1779793525,
      "updated": 1779793525
    },
    {
      "id": "6a157e6b000000000017ddf0",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "586cfba1be83a60011cafbcd",
      "created": 1779793525,
      "updated": 1779793525
    },
    {
      "id": "6a157e6b000000000017ddf1",
      "text": "code:code.text",
      "userId": "586cfba1be83a60011cafbcd",
      "created": 1779793525,
      "updated": 1779793525
    },
    {
      "id": "6a157e6b000000000017ddf2",
      "text": " 育成 (毎日のログイン動機)",
      "userId": "586cfba1be83a60011cafbcd",
      "created": 1779793525,
      "updated": 1779793525
    },
    {
      "id": "6a157e6b000000000017ddf3",
      "text": "   +",
      "userId": "586cfba1be83a60011cafbcd",
      "created": 1779793525,
      "updated": 1779793525
    },
    {
      "id": "6a157e6b000000000017ddf4",
      "text": " 闘技場オート対戦 (観戦コンテンツ)",
      "userId": "586cfba1be83a60011cafbcd",
      "created": 1779793525,
      "updated": 1779793525
    },
    {
      "id": "6a157e6b000000000017ddf5",
      "text": "   +",
      "userId": "586cfba1be83a60011cafbcd",
      "created": 1779793525,
      "updated": 1779793525
    },
    {
      "id": "6a157e6b000000000017ddf6",
      "text": " 予想ベッティング (多人数参加・社交)",
      "userId": "586cfba1be83a60011cafbcd",
      "created": 1779793525,
      "updated": 1779793525
    },
    {
      "id": "6a157e6b000000000017ddf7",
      "text": "   +",
      "userId": "586cfba1be83a60011cafbcd",
      "created": 1779793525,
      "updated": 1779793525
    },
    {
      "id": "6a157e6b000000000017ddf8",
      "text": " シーズンランキング (名誉)",
      "userId": "586cfba1be83a60011cafbcd",
      "created": 1779793525,
      "updated": 1779793525
    },
    {
      "id": "6a157e6b000000000017ddf9",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "586cfba1be83a60011cafbcd",
      "created": 1779793525,
      "updated": 1779793525
    },
    {
      "id": "6a157e6b000000000017ddfa",
      "text": "[* Bot の居場所]:",
      "userId": "586cfba1be83a60011cafbcd",
      "created": 1779793525,
      "updated": 1779793525
    },
    {
      "id": "6a157e6b000000000017ddfb",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "586cfba1be83a60011cafbcd",
      "created": 1779793525,
      "updated": 1779793525
    },
    {
      "id": "6a157e6b000000000017ddfc",
      "text": "\t予想側 Bot = オッズの流動性を供給",
      "userId": "586cfba1be83a60011cafbcd",
      "created": 1779793525,
      "updated": 1779793525
    },
    {
      "id": "6a157e6b000000000017ddfd",
      "text": "\t出走側 Bot = トーナメントの頭数を埋める / 番狂わせ演出装置",
      "userId": "586cfba1be83a60011cafbcd",
      "created": 1779793525,
      "updated": 1779793525
    },
    {
      "id": "6a157e6b000000000017ddfe",
      "text": "\t戦闘オート進行 → Bot 操作精度バレ無し",
      "userId": "586cfba1be83a60011cafbcd",
      "created": 1779793525,
      "updated": 1779793525
    },
    {
      "id": "6a157e6b000000000017ddff",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "586cfba1be83a60011cafbcd",
      "created": 1779793525,
      "updated": 1779793525
    },
    {
      "id": "6a157e6b000000000017de00",
      "text": "[*** バトル結果の設計 (7:3 ルール)]",
      "userId": "586cfba1be83a60011cafbcd",
      "created": 1779793525,
      "updated": 1779793525
    },
    {
      "id": "6a157e6b000000000017de01",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "586cfba1be83a60011cafbcd",
      "created": 1779793525,
      "updated": 1779793525
    },
    {
      "id": "6a157e6b000000000017de02",
      "text": "\t完全ステータス準拠 → 予想に迷いがなくベッティング不成立",
      "userId": "586cfba1be83a60011cafbcd",
      "created": 1779793525,
      "updated": 1779793525
    },
    {
      "id": "6a157e6b000000000017de03",
      "text": "\t完全ランダム → 育成の意味なし",
      "userId": "586cfba1be83a60011cafbcd",
      "created": 1779793525,
      "updated": 1779793525
    },
    {
      "id": "6a157e6b000000000017de04",
      "text": "\t[* 強モンスター 7 割勝つが 3 割は番狂わせ] ≒ 競馬の構造",
      "userId": "586cfba1be83a60011cafbcd",
      "created": 1779793525,
      "updated": 1779793525
    },
    {
      "id": "6a157e6b000000000017de05",
      "text": "\t属性相性 / コンディション変動 / 戦闘 AI 行動分岐ランダム",
      "userId": "586cfba1be83a60011cafbcd",
      "created": 1779793525,
      "updated": 1779793525
    },
    {
      "id": "6a157e6b000000000017de06",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "586cfba1be83a60011cafbcd",
      "created": 1779793525,
      "updated": 1779793525
    },
    {
      "id": "6a157e6b000000000017de07",
      "text": "[*** アークナイツ デュエルチャンネルのベッティングシステム]",
      "userId": "586cfba1be83a60011cafbcd",
      "created": 1779793525,
      "updated": 1779793525
    },
    {
      "id": "6a157e6b000000000017de08",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "586cfba1be83a60011cafbcd",
      "created": 1779793525,
      "updated": 1779793525
    },
    {
      "id": "6a157e6b000000000017de09",
      "text": "「敵同士のオート戦闘の勝者予想」を 3 モードに分けてある:",
      "userId": "586cfba1be83a60011cafbcd",
      "created": 1779793525,
      "updated": 1779793525
    },
    {
      "id": "6a157e6b000000000017de0a",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "586cfba1be83a60011cafbcd",
      "created": 1779793525,
      "updated": 1779793525
    },
    {
      "id": "6a157e6b000000000017de0b",
      "text": "\t[* ソロモード / ギフト対決]: 様子見 (スキップ) 可能 — カジュアル層向け",
      "userId": "586cfba1be83a60011cafbcd",
      "created": 1779793525,
      "updated": 1779793525
    },
    {
      "id": "6a157e6b000000000017de0c",
      "text": "\t[* 勝利予想対決 (30 人マッチ)]: 毎ラウンド強制予想 + ミス回数上限 = 即敗北 — ガチ勢向け",
      "userId": "586cfba1be83a60011cafbcd",
      "created": 1779793525,
      "updated": 1779793525
    },
    {
      "id": "6a157e6b000000000017de0d",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "586cfba1be83a60011cafbcd",
      "created": 1779793525,
      "updated": 1779793525
    },
    {
      "id": "6a157e6b000000000017de0e",
      "text": "[* 学び]: 同じ対戦カードでも[* ベッティングルールだけ]でカジュアル/ハードコアを分離可能。",
      "userId": "586cfba1be83a60011cafbcd",
      "created": 1779793525,
      "updated": 1779793525
    },
    {
      "id": "6a157e6b000000000017de0f",
      "text": "「全試合強制ベットか自由選択か」の二択を[* モード分離で同時実装]するパターン。",
      "userId": "586cfba1be83a60011cafbcd",
      "created": 1779793525,
      "updated": 1779793525
    },
    {
      "id": "6a157e6b000000000017de10",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "586cfba1be83a60011cafbcd",
      "created": 1779793525,
      "updated": 1779793525
    },
    {
      "id": "6a157e6b000000000017de11",
      "text": "→ 自分のゲームに適用するなら:",
      "userId": "586cfba1be83a60011cafbcd",
      "created": 1779793525,
      "updated": 1779793525
    },
    {
      "id": "6a157e6b000000000017de12",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "586cfba1be83a60011cafbcd",
      "created": 1779793525,
      "updated": 1779793525
    },
    {
      "id": "6a157e6b000000000017de13",
      "text": "\tフリー観戦モード (好きな試合だけベット) — 初心者 / Bot が混ざる場所",
      "userId": "586cfba1be83a60011cafbcd",
      "created": 1779793525,
      "updated": 1779793525
    },
    {
      "id": "6a157e6b000000000017de14",
      "text": "\tランクマッチ (N 戦は強制ベット、群集心理読み発生)",
      "userId": "586cfba1be83a60011cafbcd",
      "created": 1779793525,
      "updated": 1779793525
    },
    {
      "id": "6a157e6b000000000017de15",
      "text": "\tトーナメント (ミス制限サバイバル)",
      "userId": "586cfba1be83a60011cafbcd",
      "created": 1779793525,
      "updated": 1779793525
    },
    {
      "id": "6a157e6b000000000017de16",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "586cfba1be83a60011cafbcd",
      "created": 1779793525,
      "updated": 1779793525
    },
    {
      "id": "6a157e6b000000000017de17",
      "text": "[*** ゲームの大枠フロー (採用)]",
      "userId": "6923e3b6e09f0be0924872ef",
      "created": 1779793525,
      "updated": 1779798539
    },
    {
      "id": "6a157e6b000000000017de18",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "586cfba1be83a60011cafbcd",
      "created": 1779793525,
      "updated": 1779793525
    },
    {
      "id": "6a157e6b000000000017de19",
      "text": "1. 育てたモンスター 3 体をデッキにセット",
      "userId": "586cfba1be83a60011cafbcd",
      "created": 1779793525,
      "updated": 1779793525
    },
    {
      "id": "6a157e6b000000000017de1a",
      "text": "2. バトルにエントリー",
      "userId": "586cfba1be83a60011cafbcd",
      "created": 1779793525,
      "updated": 1779793525
    },
    {
      "id": "6a157e6b000000000017de1b",
      "text": "3. [* 毎時 00 分開幕] (人数固定待ちではない / 不足はBotで埋める)",
      "userId": "586cfba1be83a60011cafbcd",
      "created": 1779793525,
      "updated": 1779793525
    },
    {
      "id": "6a157e6b000000000017de1c",
      "text": "4. 全 10 戦のオート対戦が組まれ、対戦表公開",
      "userId": "586cfba1be83a60011cafbcd",
      "created": 1779793525,
      "updated": 1779793525
    },
    {
      "id": "6a157e6b000000000017de1d",
      "text": "5. プレイヤーはオッズを見て[* 10 戦中 5 戦まで]選んでベット",
      "userId": "586cfba1be83a60011cafbcd",
      "created": 1779793525,
      "updated": 1779793525
    },
    {
      "id": "6a157e6b000000000017de1e",
      "text": "6. ベッティング収支ランキング [* +] 育成戦績ランキングの[* 二軸]",
      "userId": "586cfba1be83a60011cafbcd",
      "created": 1779793525,
      "updated": 1779793525
    },
    {
      "id": "6a157e6b000000000017de1f",
      "text": "7. 報酬でモンスター強化",
      "userId": "586cfba1be83a60011cafbcd",
      "created": 1779793525,
      "updated": 1779793525
    },
    {
      "id": "6a157e6b000000000017de20",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "586cfba1be83a60011cafbcd",
      "created": 1779793525,
      "updated": 1779793525
    },
    {
      "id": "6a157e6b000000000017de21",
      "text": "「20 人集まったら」開幕は離脱要因 → [* 時刻トリガー + Bot 埋め]で代替する設計判断。",
      "userId": "586cfba1be83a60011cafbcd",
